    "description": "<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: .0001pt;\">At 6th level you gain resistance to your draconic damage type.</p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: .0001pt;\">In addition, whenever you fail a saving throw, you can use your reaction to roll a d4 and add it to the result of the saving throw, potentially turning it into a success.<span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\">&nbsp; </span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: .0001pt;\">You can do so a number of times equal to your proficiency bonus and regain all expended uses when you finish a short or long rest.</p>",
